    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - FULLER 10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS - PREVENTIVE MAINTENANCE -
        AIR SYSTEM
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="pm" graphiccount="0">
        <title>AIR SYSTEM</title>
        <seqlist>
            <item>
                <para>Drain moisture from the vehicle air system daily.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Listen for air leaks daily, and repair them promptly.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>If the vehicle is equipped with an air dryer, confirm that the air dryer system is working
                    properly. Repair as necessary.
                </para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Service the vehicle air compressor as required to prevent oil from entering the vehicle air
                    system.
                </para>
            </item>
        </seqlist>
    </svcproc>
